# Contributing

This repository manages the career portal for Dr. Phoebe Tsang's dental practice.

## Reporting Issues

If you notice any issues with the website, please open an issue with:
- Description of the problem
- Screenshots if applicable
- Steps to reproduce
- Expected vs actual behavior

## Development

### Prerequisites

- [Quarto](https://quarto.org/docs/get-started/) (v1.7.34 or later)
- Git

### Local Development

1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/459ecs/dental-career-opportunities.git
   cd dental-career-opportunities
   ```

2. Preview the site locally:
   ```bash
   quarto preview
   ```

3. Make your changes to `.qmd` files

4. Test the build:
   ```bash
   quarto render
   ```

### Development Documentation

See [CLAUDE.md](/CLAUDE.md) for:
- Detailed repository structure
- Content standards and conventions
- Publishing workflow
- Internal documentation security protocols

## Code of Conduct

Please maintain professional and respectful communication in all interactions related to this project.

